data.description: Hottest Deal in the neighborhood with An FHA Assumable loan at a VERY COMPETITIVE 3% Interest Rate!! This beautifully maintained, 2020 lakefront Marina model in the amenity rich community of Hampton Lakes at River Hall is priced to sell! With appealing features like its desirable split floor plan boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths and an open concept living and dining area with a large kitchen from which has views of the Extended, screened lanai overlooking the lake and yard with potential for a pool! High and dry with no damage from Ian! New paint, lighting, and gutters last year! Hampton Lakes has something for everyone! From the Zero Entry resort style pool, to the huge fitness center including yoga studio. Bocce Ball, Pickle ball, Tennis, and an open field for just plain fun, this place has the best of amenities around!!
